{"tid":2448603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華公開喺酒店隔離做啲咩　坦言想家：感覺不是那麼好","createTime":"2021-03-16T04:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T05:25:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"50cd62d51b9a23127857a37e4a2806d98cd7d959","tid":2448603,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"劉德華去年在深圳被「野生捕獲」，當時網民指他正在拍攝新戲。雖然劉德華貴為天王，但北上一樣要隔離，今日(15日)他在抖音上載一條隔離時的自拍片段，日期顯示為11月18日，劉德華在片中先除以廣東話表示隔離終於到最後一日，聲線似乎略顯疲態，他其後以國語表示今次係一個非常奇妙嘅經歷：「感覺不是那麼好，很想家，很想你們。」估唔到向來非常捱得嘅劉德華，竟然因防疫隔離而被考起。<br />\n<br />\n在影片中，只見劉德華在酒店房內放置了一個晾衫架及跑步機，另有一封手寫信，信中提到在我們成長過程中常遇到無數的惡意，如果沒人成為光帶我們走出困境，那就努力讓自己成為一道光，「你我都需要被治癒，每個人都需要鼓勵」影片上載短短數小時，已經有2百多萬點擊率。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210315/448210602448392192354796.jpeg/ZmUIg69qzW3SjqEWdcjXKIYTUDIQjE_oj_hI_4_4SP8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210315%2F448210602448392192354796.jpeg%2FZmUIg69qzW3SjqEWdcjXKIYTUDIQjE_oj_hI_4_4SP8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d0588898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210315/448209563133415424739254.jpeg/06BbXwpe_G8w5SZLecOgRrclb08RMQbPsW0meLFtJng?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210315%2F448209563133415424739254.jpeg%2F06BbXwpe_G8w5SZLecOgRrclb08RMQbPsW0meLFtJng%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=35f42dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210315/448210607112851456057483.jpeg/3cK9-wKsebbX5tWzkEfx6LPqa4N1QlrH6wVdResFXUU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210315%2F448210607112851456057483.jpeg%2F3cK9-wKsebbX5tWzkEfx6LPqa4N1QlrH6wVdResFXUU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=60ffbaff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210315/448210609264660480487321.jpeg/dH7evE_04aBWdS9vj_z9mYE18xv8wY1P_6Hl3f-h5d0?v=w1920\" d